Package: visorfuego
Title: Quarto Leaflet Viewer for Fire Risk and Active Fires
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Santiago", "Mota", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Static Quarto dashboard for AEMET fire risk maps, NASA FIRMS active fire detections, EFFIS/Copernicus WMS layers and GISCO/NUTS operational summaries and automatic FIRMS cluster alerts.
